msgstr "Este mĂłdulo define uma exceĂ§ĂŁo:"

#: ../../library/zipimport.rst:59
msgid ""
"Exception raised by zipimporter objects. It's a subclass "
"of :exc:`ImportError`, so it can be caught as :exc:`ImportError`, too."
msgstr ""
"ExceĂ§ĂŁo levantada por objetos zipimporter. Ă‰ uma subclasse "
